{"tid":1298443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【耐人尋味】TVB突然取消DSE打氣活動 考生失望問點解","createTime":"2019-07-09T01:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T02:05:56.000Z","uid":2617,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3434df2a5521512918a2d022fd106f639c647578","tid":1298443,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:26:06.000Z","msg":"【耐人尋味】TVB突然取消DSE打氣活動 考生失望問點解 (01:20)<br />\n<br />\nTVB原本於今日（9日）在apm舉行「DSE考生-放榜前的一個晚上」安排藝人與歌手為考生打氣，昨日突然在TVB的facebook宣布取消：「由於節目調動, big big channel原訂2019年7月9日晚上8時的 &ldquo;放榜前的一個晚上&rdquo;將會取消。不便之處,敬請見諒。」據知活動原本邀陳柏宇、關楚耀、麥明詩、馮盈盈、ToNick、王灝兒（JW）、Super Girls等出席，眾嘉賓昨日臨時接獲通知活動取消，並不清楚原因。<br />\n<br />\n有網民留言問點解？有表示失望，寫道：「我哋成班應屆DSE生而家都唔知點 好大壓力呀！」又有指TVB要給考生一個交代。不過，有網民問是否跟有團體發起「反紅媒遊行」有關？有人和應指DSE打氣活動年年都搞，突然取消有此地無銀之嫌。<br />\n（即時娛樂）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n而家BK同香討講兩句 個個淆底取消晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"de5cd00936d8451c87d49262aacbb5d0cf85e960","tid":1298443,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:27:17.000Z","msg":"考生 讀書讀傻左 點解都問"},{"pid":"75bd2b7efeff947ab3dcd3e8dfca5160ac27c8e1","tid":1298443,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:28:32.000Z","msg":"有壓力打個飛機好過"},{"pid":"dc2663ac66b17908cdde7744320423c019795eaf","tid":1298443,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:35:12.000Z","msg":"打少陣氣會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4940ac3fa1ba4dfc32caf017930200c9a32a5576","tid":1298443,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3434df2a5521512918a2d022fd106f639c647578","tid":1298443,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"